verses.verse: Behold <WH1288>, bless you the Lord <WH3068>, all you servants <WH5650> of the Lord <WH3068>, which by night <WH3915> stand <WH5975> in the house <WH1004> of the Lord <WH3068>.
Lift up <WH5375> your hands <WH3027> in the sanctuary <WH6944>, and bless <WH1288> the Lord <WH3068>.
The Lord <WH3068> that made <WH6213> heaven <WH8064> and earth <WH776> bless <WH1288> you out of Zion <WH6726>.
